features:

area 1 (pyramids):

- resource drain
- resource needs messaging
- launching random events
- each pyramid has an offering bar filling up 
	- each pyramid has a preferable offering type, but you can put all of them in here
	


-bonus: resource rewards (fruit growth speed up etc.)

area 2 (queue-village): 

- lining up resorces in 3 different queues 
- spawning hunters/gatherers
- sending resources to pyramids

area 3 (gathering):

- spawning resources:
	- people running around to be hunted
	- fruits growing on trees
	- wild animals running around being hunted

- hunters/gatherers going around and doing their job

